data.description: 3/2/2 Renovated Pool Home No HOA!! Gorgeous open concept eat in kitchen, formal dining, living & family room. IMPACT GLASS! Roof approx 6 years new. Custom kitchen cabinetry & quartz counter top with Pass thru. Great for BBQ's & entertaining. Double sided brick fire place in family room & kitchen. Tiles just polished. Wood flooring in sunken living & all bedrms. 2nd bedrm w/ built in murphy bed & desk. Cabana bath w/ dual sink & step in shower. Back yard with astro turf. 2 car garage w/ front loader w/d and extra refrigerator. Fully Fenced in yard great for kids & pets. Plantation shutters. RING CAMERA SYSTEM. Waterford Homes features NO HOA 3 Parks maintained by the city.  1 Blk to Publix, dining & shops! Less than 5 min to 95 & TNPKE& Sawgrass. You will LOVE this home!
